{
  "stem": "5255.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the Polish miners, they took to the German mines, and the Jewish miners that were helpers, that had something on the ball, gave-- they gave them better jobs, replacing the Polish miners that went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was lucky enough, and I was already well acquainted with the type of work to be done in the mines.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I got an excellent job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Except for, the first two days on the job, I had an accident.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A piece of coal hit me right on the nose, broke my teeth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had this kind of a face, swollen and bloody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything stopped, because I was in a special kind of situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- but this particular-- I was very lucky, because this engineer gave me a note that I am an essential worker in the mine, that I have to be back tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I asked him to give me the paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even though I didn't feel good, and I was bloodied up, and I washed myself off, and I broke a tooth, and my nose was swollen, I wanted to come back.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The reason I wanted to come back is because, anyone that got in an accident in the mines, they never returned in the mines.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because every 10 days, they used to take-- come-- came a doctor to the camp, and selected about 200 people that looked like they don't have any strength, their muscles became soft, and-- or they were in an accident.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took them to Birkenau, replaced them with newcomers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because there were constant people coming, new people coming to the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it wasn't a big thing for the Germans to replace one of these coal miners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And therefore-- and I knew about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
